casebody.data:
LZG Realty, LLC, et al., Respondents, v H.D.W. 2005 Forest, LLC, Appellant, and Eli Weinstein, et al., Respondents, et al., Defendants. (And Other Actions.) Submitted January 3, 2012; decided February 21, 2012

Reported below, 87 AD3d 727.

Motion for leave to appeal dismissed upon the ground that the order sought to be appealed from does not finally determine the actions within the meaning of the Constitution.
